-- Ballard sells fuel cell unit to Daimler and Ford
-- 
-- Thu Nov 8, 2007 12:10am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/08/us-ballard-sale-idUSWEN245320071108

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Canada's Ballard Power Systems ( BLD.TO ) on Wednesday said it agreed to sell its automotive fuel cell business to German car and truck maker Daimler ( DAIGn.DE ) and Ford Motor Co ( F.N ). 

 In a statement, Ballard said it will receive and cancel the 34.3 million Ballard shares owned by Daimler and Ford which are valued at about $168 million.